          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780804114981" href="/book/show/227676.The_Bonesetter_s_Daughter">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4091267-rebecca-huston?shelf=china">china</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4091267-rebecca-huston?shelf=2013-around-the-world-in-52-books">2013-around-the-world-in-52-books</a>, 
